  "detailed_description": "Story:<br />\r\nSome valleys on Earth have been set as target destinations for creatures teleportation from other dimensions through spacebreak of the universe. But humans did not know it, constructed the roads which became dangerous for these creatures.<br />\r\nThat is why they invited you to work as a manager of Parkland to search, collect and move these animals to the safe zone.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nContent:<br />\r\n12 of day times<br />\r\n12 vegetations<br />\r\n16 terrains<br />\r\n2304 variations<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNote:<br />\r\nWhen higher missions you earn means of transport. Firstly after all creatures were saved, later in the course of the mission and finally in the half of the mission. Lots of luck from the authors!",
  "about_the_game": "Story:<br />\r\nSome valleys on Earth have been set as target destinations for creatures teleportation from other dimensions through spacebreak of the universe. But humans did not know it, constructed the roads which became dangerous for these creatures.<br />\r\nThat is why they invited you to work as a manager of Parkland to search, collect and move these animals to the safe zone.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nContent:<br />\r\n12 of day times<br />\r\n12 vegetations<br />\r\n16 terrains<br />\r\n2304 variations<br />\r\n<br />\r\nNote:<br />\r\nWhen higher missions you earn means of transport. Firstly after all creatures were saved, later in the course of the mission and finally in the half of the mission. Lots of luck from the authors!",
